k-addons-oke-workload-identity/) |\n./COVERAGE.md:275:| `com.oracle.oci.sdk:oci-java-sdk-certificates` | [3.63.1<br>- 3.91.1](metadata/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-certificates/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> The Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Java SDK Certificates module provides client APIs and model classes for the OCI Certificates service. It lets Java applications retrieve certificate, certificate authority, and CA bundle data and list certificate bundle versions through OCI SDK clients.</details> | [100.0% (0/0 calls)](stats/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-certificates/) |\n./COVERAGE.md:276:| `com.oracle.oci.sdk:oci-java-sdk-certificatesmanagement` | [3.63.1<br>- 3.91.1](metadata/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-certificatesmanagement/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> This artifact provides the Certificates Management service module for the Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Java SDK. It supplies JVM clients, requests, responses, and models for managing OCI certificates, certificate authorities, CA bundles, associations, versions, and related lifecycle operations.</details> | [100.0% (0/0 calls)](stats/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-certificatesmanagement/) |\n./COVERAGE.md:277:| `com.oracle.oci.sdk:oci-java-sdk-circuitbreaker` | [3.63.1<br>- 3.91.1](metadata/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-circuitbreaker/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> This artifact provides the circuit breaker module used by the Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Java SDK. It wraps resilience4j circuit breaker support behind OCI SDK configuration and runtime APIs so SDK calls can fail fast when a service or endpoint is unhealthy.</details> | [100.0% (0/0 calls)](stats/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-circuitbreaker/) |\n./COVERAGE.md:278:| `com.oracle.oci.sdk:oci-java-sdk-common-httpclient-jersey3` | [3.63.1<br>- 3.91.1](metadata/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-common-httpclient-jersey3/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> The artifact provides the Jers